  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "卷八十二 王商史丹傅喜傳第五十二",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "王商字子威，涿郡蠡吾人也，徙杜陵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "商公武、武兄無故，皆以宣帝舅封。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "無故為平昌侯，武為樂昌侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "語在《外戚傳》。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "元帝崩，成帝即位，甚敬重商，徙為左將軍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "而帝元舅大司馬大將軍王鳳顓權，行多驕僭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "商論議不能平鳳，鳳知之，亦疏商。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "建始三年秋，京師民無故相驚，言大水至，百姓奔走相蹂躪、老弱號呼，長安中大亂。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "天子親御前殿，召公卿議。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "大將軍鳳以為太后與上及後宮可御船，令吏民上長安城以避水。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "群臣皆從鳳議。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "左將軍商獨曰：「自古無道之國，水猶不冒城郭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "今政治和平，世無兵革，上下相安，何因當有大水一日暴至？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "此必訛言也，不宜令上城，重驚百姓。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "上乃止。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "有頃，長安中稍定，問之，果訛言。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "上於是美壯商之固守，數稱其議。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "而鳳大慚，自恨失言。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "明年，商代匡衡為丞相，益封千戶，天子甚尊任之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "為人多質有威重，長八尺餘，身體鴻大，容貌甚過絕人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "河平四年，單于來朝，引見白虎殿。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "丞相商坐未央廷中，單于前，拜謁商。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "商起，離席與言，單于仰視商貌，大畏之，遷延卻退。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "天子聞而歎曰：「此真漢相矣！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "初，大將軍鳳連昏楊肜為琅邪太守，其郡有災害十四，已上。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "商部屬按問，鳳以曉商曰：「災異天事，非人力所為。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "肜素善吏，宜以為後。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "商不聽，竟奏免肜，奏果寢不下，鳳重以是怨商，陰求其短，使人上書言商閨門內事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "天子以為暗昧之過，不足以傷大臣，鳳固爭，下其事司隸。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "先是，皇太后嘗詔問商女，欲以備後宮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "時女病，商意亦難之，以病對，不入。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "及商以閨門事見考，自知為鳳所中，惶怖，更欲內女為援，乃因新幸李婕妤家白見其女。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "於是左將軍丹等奏：「商位三公，爵列侯，親受詔策為天下師，不遵法度以翼國家，而回辟下媚以進其私，執左道以亂政，為臣不忠，罔上不道，《甫刑》之辟，皆為上戮，罪名明白。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "臣請詔謁者召商詣若盧詔獄。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "上素重商，知匡言多險，制曰「勿治」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "鳳固爭之，於是制詔御史：「蓋丞相以德輔翼國家，典領百寮，協和萬國，為職任莫重焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "今樂昌侯商為丞相，出入五年，未聞忠言嘉謀，而有不忠執左道之辜，陷於大辟。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "前商女弟內行不修，奴賊殺人，疑商教使，為商重臣，故抑而不窮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "今或言商不以自悔而反怨懟，朕甚傷之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "惟商與先帝有外親，未忍致於理。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "其赦商罪。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "使者收丞相印綬。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "商死後，連年日蝕、地震，直臣京兆尹王章上封事召開，訟商忠直無罪，言鳳顓權蔽主。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "鳳竟以法誅章，語在《元後傳》。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "至元始中，王莽為安漢公，誅不附己者，樂昌侯安見被以罪，自殺，國除。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "自元帝為太子時，丹以父高任為中庶子，侍從十餘年。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "元帝即位，為駙馬都尉侍中，出常驂乘，甚有寵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "上以丹舊臣，皇考外屬，親信之，詔丹護太子家。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "是時，傅昭儀子定陶共王有材藝，子母俱愛幸，而太子頗有酒色之失，母王皇后無寵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "丹為人足知，愷弟愛人，貌若儻蕩不備，然心甚謹密，故尤得信於上。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "丹兄嗣父爵為侯，讓不受分。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "丹盡得父財，身又食大國邑，重以舊恩，數見褒賞，賞賜累千金，僮奴以百數，後房妻妾數十人，內奢淫，好飲酒，極滋味聲色之樂。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "為將軍前後十六年，永始中病乞骸骨，上賜策曰：「左將軍寢病不衰，願歸治疾，朕愍以官職之事久留將軍，使躬不瘳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "使光祿勳賜將軍黃金五十斤，安車駟馬，其上將軍印綬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "宜專精神，務近醫藥，以輔不衰。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "大司空何武、尚書令唐林皆上書言：「喜行義修潔，忠誠憂國，內輔之臣也，今以寢病，一旦遣歸，眾庶失望，皆曰傅氏賢子，以論議不合於定陶太后故退，百寮莫不為國恨之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "忠臣，社稷之衛，魯以季友治亂，楚以子玉輕重，魏以無忌折衝，項以范增存亡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "故楚跨有南土，帶甲百萬，鄰國不以為難，子玉為將，則文公側席而坐，及其死也，君臣相慶。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "百萬之眾，不如一賢，故秦行千金以間廉頗，漢散萬金以疏亞父。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "喜立於朝，陛下之光輝，傅氏之廢興也。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "上亦自重之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "明年正月，乃徙師丹為大司空，而拜喜為大司馬，封高武侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "丁、傅驕奢，皆嫉喜之恭儉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "又傅太后欲求稱尊號，與成帝母齊尊，喜與丞相孔光、大司空師丹共執正議。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "傅太后大怒，上不得已，先免師丹以感動喜，喜終不順。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "後數月，遂策免喜曰：「君輔政出入三年，未有昭然匡朕不逮，而本朝大臣遂其奸心，咎由君焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "其上大司馬印綬，就第。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "傅太后又自詔丞相、御史曰：「高武侯喜無功而封，內懷不忠，附下罔上，與故大司空丹同心背畔，放命圮族，虧損德化，罪惡雖在赦前，不宜奉朝請，其遣就國。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "後又欲奪喜侯，上亦不聽。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "喜在國三歲余，哀帝崩，平帝即位，王莽用事，免傅氏宮爵歸故郡，晏將妻子徙合浦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "莽白太后下詔曰：「高武侯喜姿性端愨，論議忠直。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "雖與故定陶太后有屬，終不順指從邪，介然守節，以故斥逐就國。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "傳不雲乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "『歲寒然後知松伯之後凋也』。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "其還喜長安，以故高安侯莫府賜喜，位特進，奉朝請。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "喜雖外見褒賞，孤立憂懼，後復遣就國，以壽終。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "莽賜謚曰貞侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "子嗣，莽敗乃絕。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "贊曰：自宜、元、成、哀外戚興者，許、史、三王、丁、傅之家，皆重侯累將，窮貴極富，見其位矣，未見其人也。",
          "translations": []
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "陽平之王多有材能，好事慕名，其勢尤盛，曠貴最久。",
          "translations": []
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "然至於莽，亦以覆國。",
          "translations": []
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "王商有剛毅節，廢黜以憂死，非其罪也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "史丹父子相繼，高以重厚，位至三公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "丹之輔道副主，掩惡揚美，傅會善意，雖宿儒達士無以加焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "及其歷房闥，入臥內，推至誠，犯顏色，動寤萬乘，轉移大謀，卒成太子，安母后之位。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "「無言不讎」，終獲忠貞之報。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "傅喜守節不傾，亦蒙後凋之賞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "哀、平際會，禍福速哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Chinese text: This work was published before January 1, 1923, and is in the",
          "translator": "Herbert J. Allen (1894)"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}